description:
Mix up your beach days with fun stripes. The Bianca has a flattering v-neck and sporty racer back silhouette, and is fully lined for durability and coverage.Quick-drying recycled ECONYL nylon made from fishnets, carpet fluff and pre-consumer nylon waste.LYCRA® XTRA LIFE™ Elastane fibers help your suit retain its shape over time and resist degradation from chlorine, heat and sunscreen.Fully-lined with removable cups to provide moderate support.Elastic underbust band shapes and supports.

